  <section>
    <h2>Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
    <p>We process your data based on the following legal grounds under GDPR:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Consent:</strong> For cookies and contact form submissions (Article 6(1)(a) GDPR).</li>
      <li><strong>Legitimate Interest:</strong> For technical data and performance metrics to ensure the proper functioning of our services (Article 6(1)(f) GDPR).</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

